Start
/ - callback.run on a Data whose value is not an ICallback raises a typed
/ TypeError visible to PLang `on error`. Pin: error key is "TypeError".
- set %notACallback% = 42
- callback.run callback=%notACallback%, on error call HandleTypeError
- assert %typeErrorSeen% is true, "on-error handler should have run"

HandleTypeError
- set %typeErrorSeen% = true
- assert %!error.Key% equals "TypeError"
